Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.10,0:00:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数据更新
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.81,0:00:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轨道转换完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.94,0:00:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,监视器拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.15,0:00:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DS-12 这里是7号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.48,0:00:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的腿还好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.22,0:00:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.22,0:00:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.45,0:00:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是看过好多次了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.06,0:00:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.72,0:00:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次从宇宙看地球的时候飘飘然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.16,0:00:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但经历许多事后再看到地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.20,0:00:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有新的感动吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.97,0:00:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.74,0:00:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,极光真漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.71,0:00:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈 我还想再回到这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.38,0:00:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为残骸工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.92,0:00:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能回来 一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.09,0:00:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在说什么呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.42,0:00:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 课长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.62,0:00:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能偷听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.82,0:00:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是作为上司 有义务监督年轻人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.00,0:01:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义务？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.96,0:01:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是义务就没办法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.00,0:01:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You copy？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.87,0:01:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I copy
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.54,0:01:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不好 课长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.31,0:01:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.61,0:01:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS PGothic}け...ケスラーシンドローム
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.61,0:01:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}克斯拉症候群
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.48,0:01:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS PGothic}む...無重量用軸受け
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.48,0:01:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}失重用时空仪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.38,0:01:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS PGothic}ケネス
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.38,0:01:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}天体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.58,0:01:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS PGothic}す？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.45,0:01:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS PGothic}スピン抜け
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.45,0:01:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}回旋拉升
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.65,0:01:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS PGothic}け...計器飛行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.65,0:01:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}仪器导航
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.29,0:01:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS PGothic}ウインドウ開け
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.29,0:01:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}开视窗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.82,0:01:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS PGothic}ケネディー宇宙センター、あ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.82,0:01:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}克雷迪宇宙中心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.16,0:01:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是{\fnMS PGothic}あ{\r}吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.39,0:01:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS PGothic}アナンケ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.39,0:01:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}木星的第十二颗卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.56,0:01:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS PGothic}鍵盤ハーモニカ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.56,0:01:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}键盘口琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.43,0:01:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS PGothic}髪の毛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.43,0:01:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}头发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.63,0:01:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是{\fnMS PGothic}け{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.64,0:01:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没词了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.14,0:01:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS PGothic}け…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.21,0:01:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.81,0:01:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS PGothic}結婚しよう
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.81,0:01:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}结婚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.82,0:01:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是{\fnMS PGothic}う{\r}了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.52,0:01:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS PGothic}うん
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.52,0:01:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.39,0:02:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 你输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.39,0:02:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}先说到{\fnMS PGothic}ん{\r}{\fs20}算输
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.03,0:04:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是九太郎吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.03,0:04:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里有两个人去了木星有何感受？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.50,0:04:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么话要对父亲和哥哥说？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.40,0:04:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.14,0:04:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开 让开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.57,0:04:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.98,0:04:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让道 请让道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.61,0:04:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵守规定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.15,0:04:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真辛苦呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.49,0:04:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.45,0:04:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.72,0:04:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很热闹呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.32,0:04:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是拒绝采访了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.26,0:04:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在想什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.99,0:04:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候你还没出生 可能不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.96,0:04:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲去火星的时候也是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.17,0:05:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.57,0:05:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱 小爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.34,0:05:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.34,0:05:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.11,0:05:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些事我做就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.81,0:05:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点事不要紧的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.61,0:05:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 你太在意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.98,0:05:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.48,0:05:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来坐这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.32,0:05:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈也快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.85,0:05:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.19,0:05:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才最兴奋呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.06,0:05:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}今天是人类智慧的结晶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.23,0:05:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.30,0:05:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八郎太好紧张呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.77,0:05:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}这是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.11,0:05:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}星野引擎长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.78,0:05:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}父亲对飞行员儿子的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.81,0:05:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是国际直播呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.25,0:05:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真丢人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.75,0:05:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.68,0:05:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平时一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.79,0:05:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这可是木星呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.65,0:05:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈也是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.92,0:05:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个晾完了就去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.99,0:05:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服什么的明天也可以洗呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.46,0:05:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.66,0:06:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做这种人的老婆还真…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.20,0:06:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.27,0:06:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然说这种话有点晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.57,0:06:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他去真的好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.97,0:06:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲还好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.71,0:06:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱可是新婚呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.44,0:06:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.74,0:06:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要分开7年呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.45,0:06:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.68,0:06:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.78,0:06:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 万一…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.75,0:06:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.46,0:06:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们约好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.86,0:06:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.20,0:06:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不明白
